Individual Theme Credits:
-------------------------
Each theme in themes.json includes its own credits in the meta.credits field,
attributing the original theme creators. These individual attributions are
preserved and displayed when listing themes.

The themes themselves come from various sources including but not limited to:
- iTerm2 Color Schemes (https://github.com/mbadolato/iTerm2-Color-Schemes)
- Various individual theme creators and projects
- Terminal emulator default themes

Modifications:
--------------
- Added "default" theme optimized for Atmos/Cloud Posse output
- Fixed formatting inconsistency in "Tomorrow Night Eighties" theme credits field

Note:
-----
Theme creators retain all rights to their individual color schemes. This
collection is provided as a convenience for Atmos users to enhance their
terminal experience.
